  description="The only free, local-first AI memory system with universal architecture. Works with ChatGPT, Claude, Cursor, Windsurf, VS Code, Codex, Gemini CLI, JetBrains, and 17+ AI tools. 100% local, 100% private, 100% free forever."
>
  <!-- v2.7 Announcement Banner -->
  <section style="padding: 1.25rem 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7c3aed 0%, #ec4899 100%); text-align: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <p style="color: white; margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700;">
