              <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">macOS</h3>
              <a href="https://github.com/varun369/SuperLocalMemoryV2/releases/download/v2.7.0/SuperLocalMemory-v2.7.0-macos.dmg" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
                Download DMG
