            <div class="screenshot-carousel-caption">
              <strong>Live Event Stream</strong> ‚Äî Watch every memory operation in real-time across all AI tools
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="screenshot-carousel-slide">
            <img src="/assets/screenshots/dashboard/dashboard-graph.png" alt="AI knowledge graph with automatic relationship discovery and clustering for persistent AI context" width="1200" height="750" />
            <div class="screenshot-carousel-caption">
              <strong>Knowledge Graph</strong> ‚Äî Auto-discovered relationships and community clustering
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="screenshot-carousel-slide">
            <img src="/assets/screenshots/dashboard/dashboard-agents.png" alt="Multi-agent tracking dashboard showing connected AI tools via MCP protocol with trust scores" width="1200" height="750" />
            <div class="screenshot-carousel-caption">
              <strong>Agent Tracking</strong> ‚Äî Monitor all connected AI tools and their memory activity
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="screenshot-carousel-slide">
